Utilities library used by Belledonne Communications softwares like belle-sip, mediastreamer2 and linphone.

Belongs to mbedtls (https://github.com/ARMmbed/mbedtls.git). For backward compatibility, support of polarssl is also provided.

To compile:

cmake . -DCMAKE_INSTALL_PREFIX=<install prefix>

make
make install

rpm:

make package 

options:

CMAKE_INSTALL_PREFIX :install prefix  
cmake . -DCMAKE_INSTALL_PREFIX=/opt  

CMAKE_PREFIX_PATH :search path prefix for polarssl or mbtls  
cmake . -DCMAKE_PREFIX_PATH=<polarssl or mbtls path>  

ENABLE_POLARSSL :force usage of polarssl 
cmake . -DENABLE_POLARSSL=ON -DENABLE_MBEDTLS=OFF  

ENABLE_MBEDTLS :force usage of mbed tls
cmake . -DENABLE_POLARSSL=OFF -DENABLE_MBEDTLS=OFF  
